  "text": "Polyphenols include flavonoids and tannins. Flavonoids are plant pigments which consist of two aromatic rings and an oxygen heterocycle. According to the configuration and state oxidation of the central heterocycle unit, the flavonoids are classed into eight different types: flavones, flavonols, flavonones, chalcones, isoflavones, anthocyanidins, aurones, biflavones, and neoflavonoids. Hesperetin, which is abundantly found in PF, belong to the flavonone group [CITATION_1] .",
